graph TB
    Start([New Lead]) --> Research[Stage 1: Lead Research Agent]
    
    Research --> WebSearch[Web Search Tool<br/>Company Info, News,<br/>Tech Stack, Pain Points]
    WebSearch --> ResearchData[(Research Data)]
    
    ResearchData --> Qualify[Stage 2: Qualification Agent]
    Qualify --> BANT{BANT Analysis<br/>Budget: 25pts<br/>Authority: 25pts<br/>Need: 25pts<br/>Timeline: 25pts}
    
    BANT --> Score{Total Score}
    Score -->|< 40| Unqualified[Mark as Unqualified]
    Score -->|40-59| Nurture[Move to Nurture Campaign]
    Score -->|≥ 60| Qualified[Qualified Lead]
    
    Qualified --> Outreach[Stage 3: Outreach Agent]
    Outreach --> EmailGen[Generate Personalized<br/>Email + LinkedIn Msg]
    
    EmailGen --> EmailTools{Email MCP Server}
    EmailTools --> SendEmail[Send Immediate Email]
    EmailTools --> ScheduleEmail[Schedule Follow-up<br/>+3 Days]
    
    SendEmail --> CRMUpdate[Stage 4: CRM Update]
    ScheduleEmail --> CRMUpdate
    Nurture --> CRMUpdate
    Unqualified --> CRMUpdate
    
    CRMUpdate --> CRMTools{CRM MCP Server}
    CRMTools --> CreateLead[Create/Update Lead Record]
    CRMTools --> LogActivity[Log All Activities]
    CRMTools --> SetReminder[Set Next Action]
    
    CreateLead --> Complete([Workflow Complete])
    LogActivity --> Complete
    SetReminder --> Complete
    
    Complete --> Analytics[Analytics Dashboard]
    
    style Start fill:#90EE90
    style Complete fill:#90EE90
    style Qualified fill:#FFD700
    style Unqualified fill:#FFB6C1
    style Research fill:#87CEEB
    style Qualify fill:#87CEEB
    style Outreach fill:#87CEEB
    style CRMUpdate fill:#87CEEB
    style Analytics fill:#DDA0DD
